# BROWSER-replies.md - Activity Page Reply Patterns

## S 1. Extract Unreplied Posts (Activity Page)

Navigate to `https://www.threads.net/activity/replies`, then extract with 3s embedded wait:

```javascript
browser.act({
  kind: "evaluate",
  fn: `async () => {
    await new Promise(r => setTimeout(r, 3000));
    const links = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('a[href*="/post/"]'));
    const uniqueUrls = [...new Set(links.map(l => l.href))];

    const filtered = uniqueUrls.slice(0, 10).map((url) => {
      const link = links.find(l => l.href === url);
      const container = link.parentElement.parentElement.parentElement;
      const lines = container.innerText.split('\\n').filter(l => l.trim());

      const commentIcon = container.querySelector('svg[aria-label="Reply"]');
      const iconParent = commentIcon ? commentIcon.parentElement : null;
      const iconGrandParent = iconParent ? iconParent.parentElement : null;
      const nearbyText = iconGrandParent ? iconGrandParent.innerText.trim() : '';
      const hasReplyNumber = /^\\d+$/.test(nearbyText);

      return {
        url: url,
        author: lines[0] || 'unknown',
        preview: lines.slice(2).join(' ').slice(0, 200),
        alreadyReplied: hasReplyNumber
      };
    }).filter(item => item.author !== '{{handle_slug}}' && !item.alreadyReplied);

    return filtered;
  }`,
  profile: "{{browser_profile}}"
})
```

